title: NetExtender Mac OS X 8.0.785 Dell SonicWall VPN client
description:
You may think you need this, but you probably don't.  It doesn't work post-El Capitan Mac OS X 10.11

What you really need to do is download the SonicWall Mobile Connect from the Mac App store.  Despite its misleading name, it will work on Mac OS X, not just on iOS devices.

Unless you're running pre-El Capitan OS X, in which case, have at it.  I thought this was a little difficult to find on the net, so I'm posting it here
